            "varname": "redfish_logservices_max_age",
            "caption": "Redfish Logservices: Max Age",
            "description": "Age out SEL entries older than this many days: they are no longer alerted on, only counted in the summary. A controller keeps an entry until the log is cleared, so a long-since resolved event would otherwise keep the check in a non-OK state forever.",
